'''Aran''' could refer to several individuals:

*'''[[Aran (Elomin)|Aran]]''', a secret informant for the [[Alliance to Restore the Republic|Rebel Alliance]].
*'''[[Aran Cho]]''', a [[Captain/Legends|captain]] in the [[Imperial Navy/Legends|Imperial Navy]].
*'''[[List of computer-controlled character names in Battlefront games|Aran Nomante]]''', one of many computer-controlled Rebels in [[Star Wars: Battlefront|the]] [[Star Wars: Battlefront II|battlefront]] [[Star Wars Battlefront: Renegade Squadron|games]].
*'''[[Aran Starfire]]''', founder of the [[Gellefon Freedom Fighters]].
